summary:
An entrepreneurial sustainability and urban development professional.

I flourish in dynamic, high-paced and creative environments and am passionate about working towards a world in which sustainability is the status quo, by communicating about it in an attractive way.

Characterized by a result-oriented, perseverant and efficient working style.
